<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3437] Allow Explicit Splits from the Shell</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3437</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no way currently to issue explicit splits from the shell.   You can only accomplish it through HBaseAdmin currently.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
